text.tspan: Database engines use rewrite rules to improve the performance of SQL queries.
In practice, these rules are not verified, leading to costly bugs.
We provide a tool, VeriCQ, to efficiently and automatically check the
correctness of conjunctive SQL query rewrites. VeriCQ is verified in Coq.
Using a SAT solver to proof query equivalence leads to significant speadups over
brute force search, on medium and large queries.
